  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0dc0\u0daf\u0dcf\u0db1\u0db8\u0dca \u0d9c\u0db8\u0db1\u0d9a",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Students on a risky journey",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A group of students studying at Bharathi Vidyalaya, Badulla went on a dangerous journey on the roof of a private bus traveling from Badulla to Allerawa without any facilities to go home after school.",
        "SLTB buses are also not running due to the tire battery crisis and private buses without diesel have been disrupted.",
        "Students who come to school find it very difficult to get back home after school without buses."
      ],
